Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:06.28,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:06.28,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:12.72,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:12.72,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:27.34,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:27.34,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:39.08,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:39.08,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:44.59,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:44.59,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:50.09,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:50.09,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:56.37,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:56.37,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:01.67,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:01.67,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:07.38,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:07.38,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:11.15,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:11.15,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:41.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:50.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, I'd thought that a grown-up woman\Nwould no longer sing songs for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:59.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. We were celebrating the end of our assignment...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Blanket?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:27.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a song from an old movie that I'd seen on video before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:30.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I held my breath and listened to that voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:35.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...which seemed like it would fade away\Nif she moved even a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:39.43,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you just tell her that you like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.97,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.44,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\bord1\shad0\pos(627,47)\be1\c&HA49DD0&\3c&H486367&}thump
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:52.44,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\bord1\shad0\pos(76,47)\be1\3c&H486367&\c&H8780C1&}thump
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.69,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see you, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:12.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:28.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Can you come over? I've brought back the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:33.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry it. It goes to the archives, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:34.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:38.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And please hand this to Tsukamoto-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:41.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go stop by Hanamoto-kun's now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:43.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika-san, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:48.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the other day. I've added a 30% bonus to your wage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:50.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, we'll be okay for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:52.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck with your graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:58.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're not coming to the ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:03:59.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:03.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you to hand this to Kyoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give it to her along with the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And please congratulate Hashimoto-kun for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:10.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:15.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so strange that you're teaching here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:19.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm speaking face to face with you like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:22.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it's been so many years since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:28.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This room still has the same sunlight and scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels as if everyone is still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:37.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Rika, what are you going to do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows. I haven't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:42.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't he waiting for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:56.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:05:00.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Hanamoto-kun offered me a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:04.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get a new pattern book for wallpapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and I've been forgetting to tell you this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:13.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Asai-san from Artcraft, who we worked with the other day,\Nwas saying that he got the tickets for the soccer game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He was saying that he'd get in touch with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:26.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with that? Won't the other company get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:27.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, then that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better for him to have many options.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He should decide for himself when it\Ncomes to something this important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself, Iron Lady! I don't want to see you like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Captain Broken Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you calling Captain Broken Heart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:48.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Lady, your panties are a little childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:56.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Patrasche... it's a Rubens painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:59.04,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H635514&\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}In the anime version of Dog of Flanders, Nello and\N{\be0\3c&H635514&}Patrasche{\be1\3c&H000000&} die in front of the {\be1\3c&H000000&}Paul Rubens painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:57.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, his soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Push it back in, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll put a blemish on the Iron Lady's background!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we'll meet at the bowling alley in Nakano.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:12.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, that's far away! Are we drinking after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is Takiguchi-kun coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:18.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your change is 240 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:19.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you want to come, Hanamoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:24.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You never come to something like this, so how about giving it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:28.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but Hanamoto-san needs to work on her piece, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:35.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Your piece for the art museum was\Neven featured in the newspaper the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:38.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing. Your next one's going to be for a gallery, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:42.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Takazawa was talking happily about it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:45.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't interfere with Hanamoto's work," he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't speak much, you sure are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:49.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably not interested in socials, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.51,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's for a gallery, then a statue won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:55.06,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,About tendencies...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.52,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Going overseas while you're young will give you a wider perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.60,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,When will your next work be completed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:02.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Hanamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:05.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:06.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:08.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:28.55,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamoto-san needs to work on her piece, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.55,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,When will your next work be completed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.09,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an offer to make a documentary about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:33.26,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamoto-san, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.26,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Win an award while you're at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.47,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,She's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.43,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough pieces to make a personal exhibit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.18,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try studying in Europe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:48.69,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Hagu. Just make what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:53.16,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Shape your thoughts and feelings into your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:58.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are! I've found the Korobokkur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hairstyle is good! Ring, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tail, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:05.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouse shoes, ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:08.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,From today, you are Nezumi Mouse No. 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:08.00,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,50)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Nezumi: {\be1\3c&H000000&}mouse in Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come into the ring and duke it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:11.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouse No. 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:13.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:14.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this scratch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:20.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san? Hagu-chan, is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:24.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takemoto, Mouse No. 1 isn't moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:30.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san, could it be that you bullied her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:31.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:33.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:35.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouse No. 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:44.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, hold on for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I-I need to go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:53.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be all right. It's okay. Just let it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:56.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Mouse No. 1 and Takemoto go...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:02.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Morita!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:06.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who stole the lumber\Nfrom the archive room, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:11.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pops, now isn't the time for that... Mouse No. 1 is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this Mouse No. 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen seriously to what I'm saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:18.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you waste your talent on this silliness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:32.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamoto-sensei said he'll be here in about twenty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can she sleep for a while longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:40.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. It must be tough for her, though.\NThis is her third time this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That often? But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply, it's due to stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it seems that she's always been sickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:54.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no easy task to bear the weight of all the expectations\Nplaced on you and still manage to keep your own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:58.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's the job of the adults around her to assist her in that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:05.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not easy for the other students to see her being so sheltered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:10.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Some shun her, while others may vent their frustration on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:12.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.92,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching Hagu-chan made me fret a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:22.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I think she's a happy girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She has people by her side looking after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:33.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:36.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being late, Dr. Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:37.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I've caused you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. This is my job, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:46.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you also, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:49.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:11:02.85,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he'd like to become Hagu just once,\Nto see the world through her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.43,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,"I wonder what it would look like," he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:13.65,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the moon that I see is different\Nfrom the one that Hagu-chan sees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:22.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:25.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:32.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Hagu. It's your favorite huge moon, hanging low.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it pretty, Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:12:02.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is the May Sickness, then I guess\NI have the December Sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:12:02.49,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}May Sickness: {\be1\3c&H000000&}the depression that newcomers experience in\NMay, a month after admission to college of employment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but I feel anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The colorful illumination and the sound of the bells...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a place for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:16.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels as if they're asking those questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I need to get ahold of myself! I'm not a kid anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:21.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:27.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-M-Morita-san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:30.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Adieu!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,An invitation to a Christmas party?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:36.27,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}In Japan, Christmas is\Ncelebrated on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:36.27,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.5\be1\c&HAAA9D4&\fs32\shad0\frz-19\3c&H888CA9&\pos(257,325)}Christmas Party
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:36.27,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1.5\shad0\frz-19\c&HF0F5FB&\3c&HCACCD7&\pos(240,341)}Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:36.27,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H959A9E&\be1\shad0\bord0.5\frz-19\fscy150\pos(223,376)\c&H939297&}12/24 7pm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:36.27,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H959A9E&\be1\shad0\fs24\fscx83\bord0.5\b0\frz-20\pos(316,452)\c&HA7A7AA&}Location: Hanamoto Seminar Room\NBring Your Own Presents
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A Christmas party?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:43.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I have a Christmas party with\Nmy friends when I'm already 22?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:47.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's on the Eve, at that! I have better things to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas party?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:56.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he came... wearing a Santa costume at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:13:00.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And for some reason, the location is this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:06.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But, "bring your own snacks" and\N"bring your own presents for a gift exchange"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:10.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that guy so childish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:11.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:14.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaaaay! It's a Christmas party!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:20.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it makes Hagu happy, well, I'll be okay with it... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A Christmas party?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:28.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... I don't have any plans for the 24th yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:33.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think I'll go... Mayama will be coming too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:37.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go, it'll make him uncomfortable, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:38.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The scent of love...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me smell it! The scent of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:46.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:48.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:48.51,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\c&H4C509D&\fs38\an4\shad0\bord0.3\pos(398,32)\3c&H504EA3&}Iron
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A point for the Iron Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray for the Iron Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The Iron Lady is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray for the Iron Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:58.35,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fry12\frz21\shad0\bord1.5\move(230,210,230,-18)\fad(1000,0)\fs30\c&H365B99&\3c&HB5CEDE&}Central Avenue
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:14:00.77,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,300)\c&F000000&\shad0\fs44\pos(444,450)\3c&HE9F0F0&}December 24th
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:04.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,10,000 yen, 10,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:07.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan gave me 10,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I should eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are seven people in all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:16.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A roasted drumstick, flan, or tiramisu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:15.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that would be enough for all and feels like Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:18.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really think of anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:23.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas... isn't fun for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:29.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not like that. I'm sorry, I spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:38.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah... To be honest, I don't really like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:43.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I lived with just my mom, and she was a nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:49.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So every year I attended the Christmas party\Nin the pediatric ward at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:55.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But even though everyone was acting cheerful, Christmas\Nat the hospital had its unique atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:57.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being late, Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:06.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:09.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:14.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:16.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:21.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, what's the matter? Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:27.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So during Christmas, I automatically\Nsmell the scent of disinfectants...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:34.45,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,No... that pungent odor is probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What a huge ham roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:37.12,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\shad0\fnAlsina Ultrajada\be1\fscy80\fs50\c&HA1DEE7&\frz20.357\pos(235,118)\3c&H7FB0BE&}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:37.29,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\shad0\fnAlsina Ultrajada\be1\fscy80\fs50\c&HA1DEE7&\frz20.357\pos(235,118)\3c&H7FB0BE&}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like ham? Or cheese?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:41.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken drumsticks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:46.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you like? What do you want to\Neat? Seaweed-wrapped rice crackers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you want to grill some mochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:51.43,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that she's trying to cheer me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, and... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:57.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's buy a ton of stuff and get ready for the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:57.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Hagu-chan, do you like spaghetti?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:01.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for making you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:12.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:18.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That car over there is Hanamoto-sensei's, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:20.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... what is it, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be working...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:26.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some refreshments.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have them in the car, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:44.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's in that paper bag? It smells like coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:47.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-kun brought it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:50.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's in a stainless steel thermo mug.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still hot... would you like some, Hanamoto-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:04.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:08.79,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord1.5\be1\fs60\move(223,84,502,84)\c&H4F51BC&\3c&HC0CEFB&}Spaghetti
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:08.79,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H4652B9&\shad0\be1\fs31\move(621,155,874,155)\3c&HC0CEFB&}napolitana
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:07.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.79,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H4652B9&\shad0\be1\fs31\move(486,231,682,231)\3c&HC0CEFB&}salted cod roe
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:08.79,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H4652B9&\shad0\be1\fs31\move(314,202,469,202)\3c&HC0CEFB&}carbonara
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.79,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H4652B9&\shad0\be1\fs31\move(184,251,298,251)\3c&HC0CEFB&}meat sauce
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:08.79,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H4652B9&\shad0\be1\fs31\move(131,189,202,189)\3c&HC0CEFB&}mushroom sauce
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure put some thought into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:12.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo. Is it okay if my sister joins too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is this mountain of croquettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:17.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we supposed to do with all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:19.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I even brought two cabbages!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabbages?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:27.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:29.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to make us some salads, Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:36.03,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&F000000&\bord0\shad0\an3\pos(595,419)}salt
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:36.53,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&F000000&\bord0\shad0\an3\pos(595,419)}salt
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:37.03,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&F000000&\bord0\shad0\an3\pos(595,419)}salt
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:37.53,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&F000000&\bord0\shad0\an3\pos(595,419)}salt
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:37.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a man's dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:45.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:51.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's some more food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:55.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you came after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:57.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you turned down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:02.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so Yamada is here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:05.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What, am I not supposed to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:03.39,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.5\be1\shad0\pos(642,160)\c&H545AAB&\3c&H5D6791&}Non-alcoholic
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:04.27,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.5\be1\shad0\pos(642,160)\3c&H5D6791&\c&H5E5EA5&}Non-alcoholic
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.06,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.5\be1\shad0\pos(642,160)\c&H5E5EA5&\3c&H5D6791&}Non-alcoholic
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine. It's perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:11.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, stop drinking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:13.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lie down for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:20.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Mayama, you idiot... I can drink more...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:30.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful legs...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:35.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, both of you will have legs\Nlike this when you grow up... see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:41.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:44.40,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,This is truly a scene straight out of hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:46.65,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have come...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:53.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Rika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:55.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's at her husband's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Mayama, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:06.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew about it all already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:09.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Rika talk to you about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:11.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. But little by little...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:14.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a year and a half since I started going there, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:16.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:21.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:34.49,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}mite minu furi no mainichi ni naresugite boku wa miushinatta
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:34.49,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Too used to spend my days pretending not to see, I've lost my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:26.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:34.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why don't we eat some cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:35.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:47.04,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}gara ni mo naku kyou kimi no yasashii kotoba ni jibun wo hidoku hajita
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:47.04,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But today, your unusually kind words made me really ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:39.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:45.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's almost midnight, why don't we drive the girls back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:57.05,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}suiheisen no mukougawa ga maru de nozokeru gurai
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:57.05,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The sky's too clear and without a single cloud...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, where does that girl live?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:53.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she lives across from the driving school at Kubo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:56.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a liquor store next to the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:57.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada Liquor Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:05.23,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}haresugita sora kageri wa hitotsu sae nai
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:05.23,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As if I can see beyond the horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:00.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, thanks for doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:05.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry, but can you clean up a bit and lock the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.56,0:20:06.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:07.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:21.95,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}dareka ga boku wo kegashita dakara boku mo hito wo uragittekita
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:21.95,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someone disgraced me, so I've been betraying others too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:34.92,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ai no katachi wo baka rashii tsukurimono da to kosokoso waratta
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:34.92,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've been quietly laughing at the silliness of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:32.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:35.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? You were awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:37.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:41.22,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}tooku de hakou ga yureteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:41.22,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The waves are shimmering in the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:42.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now. You're a lightweight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:48.44,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}mou kanashii koto mo subarashii koto mo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:48.44,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to stamp down upon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:51.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:53.65,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}muriyari fumitsubushitakunai
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:53.65,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Neither the sad nor wonderful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:53.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at his grin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:56.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be having a fun dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:21:00.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of spiteful, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:05.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:07.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's sparkly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:13.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really... really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:16.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:27.85,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}akanai mabuta kosutte mieru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:27.85,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I rub my heavy eyelids to reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:32.98,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}pastel moyou no mirai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:32.98,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}A future in the shape of pastels
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:40.12,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}chiribamerareta kigou o tadoru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:40.12,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I follow the scattered symbols
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:44.20,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}taguri yoseta hyoujou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:44.20,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}As my expressions were pulled in closer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:49.96,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}nee nandakke sagashiteita mono
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:49.96,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Say, what was it that we were looking for again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:53.04,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}are wa soune itsudakke
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.50,0:21:53.04,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}That's right, exactly when were those days
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.00,0:22:00.43,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}bokura ga inryoku ni sakarai nagara deatta koro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:22:00.43,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}When we used to meet, denying the attraction\Nthat was forming between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:06.35,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sore ga waltz no you dane fushigi sa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:06.35,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}It's like a waltz, isn't it? It's quite marveling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:12.56,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sasayaku youna komorebi no kousaten de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:12.56,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}We paint away sceneries
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:18.78,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}futari waltz no youni ne mawari nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:18.78,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}As we waltz and spin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.99,0:22:24.91,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}egaki dashite yuku mono
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.99,0:22:24.91,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}Where the whispering sunlight falls through the trees and meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.71,0:22:33.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Thinking about my mother back home.
